name: Mr Foofarpaw
description:
Done in 48 hours at Chillennium 2016. Mr. Foofarpaw the cat is stuck in a tree. You've rescued dozens of cats before, so there's no need to make a big fuss about this cat, right?

Made by the members of Team Duck Sandwich:

  • Rachel Maduro - Art, Sound
  • Roger Villanueva - Programming, Enemy AI
  • Gerald Hu - Programming, Animations
  • Eric Buxkemper - Programming, Level Generation
